OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSecond homes in Wales could
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fface 300% council tax hikes
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some second home owners in Wales could 
OL,6, pay four times their current level of  
OL,7, council tax from next year, the Welsh  
OL,8, government has announced.              
OL,10,FCurrently councils can charge a second 
OL,11,Fhome premium of up to 100% but that    
OL,12,Fwill increase to 300% from April 2023. 
OL,14,FThe move, included in a Labour-Plaid   
OL,15,FCymru cooperation agreement, is part of
OL,16,Fefforts to make it easier for people to
OL,17,Fafford homes where they grew up.       
OL,19,FA homeowners' group said the move was  
OL,20,F"morally indefensible".                
